### Timezone Setting ###
timezone: Asia/Tokyo

### Schedule Setting ###
schedule:
  cron>: 0 8 * * *

### Manage Workflows ###
+_p100__data_preparation:
  require>: _p100__data_preparation
  session_time: ${moment(session_date).format()}
  rerun_on: all

+_p200__parent_segment_update:
  require>: _p200__parent_segment_update
  session_time: ${moment(session_date).format()}
  rerun_on: all

